{"tid":589378,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"日農民請超級怪獸狼守田　雙眼發光「講人話」專嚇野豬","createTime":"2018-03-12T00:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T15:55:57.000Z","uid":81228,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2f588c30a5f5091a6c82b963e633a8a1d3c06da2","tid":589378,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T00:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/167157/thumbnail/12ea838d57c9840f30cbb5c91c24c779.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F167157%2Fthumbnail%2F12ea838d57c9840f30cbb5c91c24c779.jpg&h=2ab95ab6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本不少農地因人口減少，在沒有人看守下，遭野豬入侵吃掉農作物，造成嚴重損失。半年前各縣農田引入名叫「超級怪獸狼」（Super Monster Wolf）的機械狼代替稻草人，其雙眼可發出紅光，身軀閃藍光，它更會大聲怪叫。經過半年以上的實驗，日本農協宣布機械狼有效驅趕不速之客，並將於下月投入量產，叫價每台約3.8萬港元。不少網民看到機械狼後，均指其外表恐怖得連人也會被嚇走，又指它像宮崎駿動畫《幽靈公主》中的麒麟獸。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268526/xlarge/8656a3345a3f9a8fb8d043b1a2c3dfb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268526%2Fxlarge%2F8656a3345a3f9a8fb8d043b1a2c3dfb8.jpg&h=cac5edb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「超級怪獸狼」去年7月被設置於日本千葉縣木更津市一處稻田及栗子林之中，成功趕走了不少野豬。（視覺中國）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268540/xlarge/ef97752f7c11473c21092dc3360d2bbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268540%2Fxlarge%2Fef97752f7c11473c21092dc3360d2bbe.jpg&h=558a009b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268539/xlarge/4b9967cbf3d75ca95e8be2de9443b378.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268539%2Fxlarge%2F4b9967cbf3d75ca95e8be2de9443b378.jpg&h=f9e64768&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268547/xlarge/f164645cef81b5077762828c0212702f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268547%2Fxlarge%2Ff164645cef81b5077762828c0212702f.jpg&h=2e22b0a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268543/xlarge/0d42836456c8975402971c8c6ceea875.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268543%2Fxlarge%2F0d42836456c8975402971c8c6ceea875.jpg&h=f4edab72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268556/xlarge/805df7edb05bd203bdf639d5bd7348d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268556%2Fxlarge%2F805df7edb05bd203bdf639d5bd7348d8.jpg&h=73111350&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268541/xlarge/fe7cd512a13c8c0d00b99983c6b80c6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268541%2Fxlarge%2Ffe7cd512a13c8c0d00b99983c6b80c6a.jpg&h=c08ac86d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268545/xlarge/536e42e7a7d8c42c4709a3a229f6b538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268545%2Fxlarge%2F536e42e7a7d8c42c4709a3a229f6b538.jpg&h=89811763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268544/xlarge/f5cd4b4904488804c46d1b78308cbbed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268544%2Fxlarge%2Ff5cd4b4904488804c46d1b78308cbbed.jpg&h=c7cbf45b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268546/xlarge/e85ee3105a8c381e52ce3c56ee003a2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268546%2Fxlarge%2Fe85ee3105a8c381e52ce3c56ee003a2a.jpg&h=bfbbad67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268549/xlarge/d5c6f237486d26e8aab0219621e7bf9a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268549%2Fxlarge%2Fd5c6f237486d26e8aab0219621e7bf9a.jpg&h=0764027f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268550/xlarge/181f6d813a5ce090fef0a60d4222deb8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268550%2Fxlarge%2F181f6d813a5ce090fef0a60d4222deb8.jpg&h=27cc5ad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268548/xlarge/dd00659cec79298c3df453820662d652.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268548%2Fxlarge%2Fdd00659cec79298c3df453820662d652.jpg&h=1373b279&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268552/xlarge/94d8df6892c122d0ceac0bde64f72e2f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268552%2Fxlarge%2F94d8df6892c122d0ceac0bde64f72e2f.jpg&h=2114949d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268551/xlarge/3e9cfb1aa64a004c3b6acebc0944b51b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268551%2Fxlarge%2F3e9cfb1aa64a004c3b6acebc0944b51b.jpg&h=d282128a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268553/xlarge/a7323bee770256e752880dd1066f654e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268553%2Fxlarge%2Fa7323bee770256e752880dd1066f654e.jpg&h=7202d948&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268554/xlarge/17005cebbb42e3e882ef9ccdba8c1d4e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268554%2Fxlarge%2F17005cebbb42e3e882ef9ccdba8c1d4e.jpg&h=a4b537ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268555/xlarge/4fd2bed2cbc7e851d7107c0d946dcdef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268555%2Fxlarge%2F4fd2bed2cbc7e851d7107c0d946dcdef.jpg&h=a2d1c1f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268561/xlarge/61c140855e4481511034e9ecac76ccf7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268561%2Fxlarge%2F61c140855e4481511034e9ecac76ccf7.jpg&h=acc4f5ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去年7月，「超級怪獸狼」被設置於日本千葉縣木更津市一處稻田及栗子林之中，成功趕走不少野豬。以往該稻田曾被野豬破壞至無法收割，原本可生產3噸栗子的栗子林，產量亦跌至不到2噸，但獲機械狼保護後，收成回復正常，而且栗子場的產量亦回升至2噸以上。<br />\n<br />\n除千葉縣的農地，「超級怪獸狼」亦被放到北海道及山梨縣等7個不同地方，成功阻止野生動物進入高爾夫球場翻土，及減少鹿闖入高速公路交匯處。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268525/xlarge/c2ae756802db825fa55e3c0181bb023c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268525%2Fxlarge%2Fc2ae756802db825fa55e3c0181bb023c.jpg&h=a62ecbed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「超級怪獸狼」（Super Monster Wolf）除了雙眼能發出紅光，身軀閃出藍光，它更會大聲怪叫。（網上片段截圖）<br />\n<br />\n生產商「太田精器」下月將大量生產「超級怪獸狼」，預計售價每隻51.4萬日元（約3.8萬港元）。生產商指，如果農民無法負擔此價錢，他們亦能提供月租服務。<br />\n<br />\n「超級怪獸狼」由北海道大學和太田精器花了約7年時間研發製造，怪獸狼身體長65厘米、高50厘米（包含腳部支撐架），利用太陽能充電池供電，身上鋪上仿真毛髮，配合紅外線裝置可以偵測直徑一公里內的移動物體。<br />\n<br />\n怪獸狼雖然不能走動，但偵測到動物靠近後，其頭部會自動轉向，啟動眼部的紅色LED燈，並發出最高達90分貝的怪叫，最遠能傳遍1平方公里。怪獸狼不但可以模仿狼叫，更可發出槍聲、警笛聲及人聲等48種聲音。太田精器指，怪獸狼比電網更有用，播放不同聲音可以防止動物習以為常，從而有效驅趕牠們，廣播人話亦可防小偷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1268527/xlarge/fe0a08bf1073bff6b2ca5c10e1ade511.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1268527%2Fxlarge%2Ffe0a08bf1073bff6b2ca5c10e1ade511.jpg&h=969e8a66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「超級怪獸狼」去年7月被設置於日本千葉縣木更津市一處稻田及栗子林之中，成功趕走了不少野豬。（視覺中國）<br />\n<br />\n木更津市農業協同組合代表理事組合長梅澤千加夫指，農協將成為縣內販售「超級怪獸狼」的代理，期待生產商將機械狼的性能進一步提升，「希望頸部可以360旋轉，在路軌上移動，將它變成「超級無敵怪獸狼」（Ultra Super Monster Wolf）。<br />\n<br />\n不少日本網民看到機械狼後，均指其外表太恐怖，「連人也會被嚇走」，又指它像宮崎駿動畫《幽靈公主》中的麒麟獸。日本作為動漫之國，有網民更發揮無限想像力，提議讓「無頭騎士」騎在「超級怪獸狼」上。<br />\n<br />\n（朝日新聞、英國廣播公司）<br />\n撰文：溫嘉敏<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1/167157/%E8%90%BD%E5%AF%A6%E9%87%8F%E7%94%A2-%E6%97%A5%E8%BE%B2%E6%B0%